1. Sunce je danas jako (*suncu*). (The sun is very bright today.)
2. Gledam (*suncu*) u lice. (I'm looking at the sun in the face.)
3. Naše polje je izloženo (*suncu*). (Our field is exposed to the sun.)
4. Nalazi se na samom (*suncu*). (It's located right in the sun.)
5. Životinje su se sklonile od (*suncu*). (The animals have moved away from the sun.)
6. Od (*sunca*) se ne može pobeći. (You can't escape from the sun.)
7. Čovek zavisi od (*sunca*) za preživljavanje. (Man depends on the sun for survival.)
8. Neki ljudi se sunčaju kako bi dobili boju (*suncu*). (Some people sunbathe to get a tan from the sun.)
9. Zaštitite kožu od štetnih zraka (*sunca*). (Protect your skin from harmful sun rays.)
10. Deca vole da se igraju na (*suncu*). (Kids love to play in the sun.)

(Note: I added the word "sun rays" in the translation of the ninth sentence to better reflect the original meaning of the sentence.)